 Bhakti pleads that the Gokuldham residents allow her to spend the night since she had a dream about Ganesha paying her a visit and happily doing the Garba with her. snippet.title: Israel 'ready for war' after Hamas infiltration and 5,000 rockets in 20 minutes
snippet.description:
The Israeli Defence Forces has declared a â€œstate of readiness for warâ€ and vowed that â€œIsrael will winâ€ after Hamas launched a surprise attack on Israel this morning.

The centre and south of Israel have been under sustained rocket fire for more than three and a half hours according to Israeli media. Earlier armed gunmen reportedly infiltrated Israeli communities after crossing the border fence.

Hamas has so far taken 35 Israeli hostages, according to Israel media. At least five Israelis are thought to have been killed and at least 100 hundred more injured.

Defense Minister Yoav Gallant warned that Hamas â€œmade a grave mistakeâ€ in one of the most serious escalations of the conflict in years.

â€œToday the people are regaining their revolution,â€ leader of Hamasâ€™ military wing Mohammed Deif said in the recorded message, as he called on Palestinians from east Jerusalem to northern Israel to join the fight and â€œexpel the occupiers and demolish the walls.â€

Everyone at Gokuldham is relieved when Bhakti regains consciousness, but they are surprised to hear something new about her. Bhide is certain of his decision since he does not want to jeopardize the safety of the gold chain and silver modak. Watch the episode to find out if Bhakti's request is granted.

To the principal ji, gaur naal suno gall ji.
College ch saal mera aakhari, haul pende ajkal ji. Zara nigah maro sade wal ji.
Visha aarzi da yaara diya yaariyan, iss aarzi nu kro parvaan ji. Gaal modeyo na dil fail honge. Pass kr lange sare imtihan ji.
Hove na dilan da nuksan ji, enna tusi rakhao  dhyan ji, shreeman ji. Meri binti management nu, sada camp ek hor lagva dio. Dur lejo ji phadan val nu, yaadgari  photoaan vi krva dao. Sade sera toh thakan jehi la dao.

I beg to say time very less jii. Sach akhdaan mazak ni mein karda. Tussi maapeya jahe ho saade guru ho, todhi  nuhn bina ve na mera sarda. Sacche dilon ohde utte marda. Teen saal toh pyaar ohnu  krda.
Ek bojh hai kitaaban da dimaag teh, dujha  maarle vichodeya de darr ne. Tussi khudh  dekhi college di zindagi tuhade bina sade dukh kinne harne.
Dilan ne ve laaye paane dharne, kidda masla  gambhir khada dekhlo. Kro hukum tan hove haal ji.

To the principal jii, hun meenta te aagyi gaal ji. Seva vekhe aa principal ji meenta teh aagyi gaal ji.
College ch saal mera aakhari haul pende aajkal ji, zara nigha maro saade val jii.

Dilan ne ve laaye paane dharne, kidda masla  gambhir khada dekhlo. Kro hukum tan hove haal ji.

To the principal jii, hun meenta te aagyi gaal ji. Seva vekhe aa principal ji meenta teh aagyi gaal ji.
College ch saal mera aakhari haul pende aajkal ji, zara nigha maro saade val jii.

snippet.title: The Apartment | EP 02 | Ft. Abhirami Venkatachalam, Ajay Melvin | Tamil Web Series | JFW | 4K
snippet.description:
The Apartment - A Story of a Mismatched Couple is a 6 episode tamil web series by JFW featuring Abhirami Venkatachalam and Ajay Melvin!  Get ready to fall in love with the quirkiest Rom Com Duo as we introduce Sam and Vidya whose unique chemistry promises to make this story one for the ages!

Episode 2 - Vivid Dream
Sam and Vidya are caught spending the night together by Preethi and Vinodh which takes them by surprise! What happened the previous night? Will Vidya stay longer than expected? All this and more in the second episode of "The Apartment"

#jfw #jfworiginals #jfwwebseries #theapartment #romcom #romanticcomedy #abhiramivenkatachalam #abhirami #ajay #ajaymelvin #leo #leotrailer #vijay #trisha 

Episode 1 - https://youtu.be/Z6jYeti1pmU

Abhirami Venkatachalam is an Indian actress and model known for her work in the Tamil film industry. She gained recognition for her role in the Tamil film "Nerkonda Paarvai" alongside actor Ajith Kumar and garnered love from the audience for being a fierce participant in Bigg Boss.

Watch the first episode and let us know your thoughts in the comments section below!

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.
